Class _Tester2

java.lang.Object
_Tester2
public class _Tester2 extends Object
The _Tester2 class is designed to test the Advisor, Student, and Courses class but most importantly asks as the backbone connecting the frontend and backend together. If I had more time, it would be called the "backbone" or something more related to the backend. Creates an array of 5 advisors which has their basic information, and each advisor contains 3 students where each student has at least one course each semester. Words with a frontend GUI consisting of Java swing and Java AWT components.
